{"tid":2434737,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲公佈現代製造倡議 挑戰中共供應鏈","createTime":"2021-03-05T17:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T17:43:04.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e6eb73fa6ba2fedbcdf0c24b48c0ef17e42f80e6","tid":2434737,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T17:12:12.000Z","msg":"澳洲與中國大陸關係緊張之際，澳洲政府週四（4日）公佈總值13億澳元（約78.5億港元）的「現代製造倡議」的10年路線圖。<br />\n<br />\n該希望通過提高加工和製造水平，在潔淨能源轉型關鍵產品供應及礦物供應鏈方面可與中國大陸競爭。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲是電池關鍵材料金屬鋰的最大出口國，亦是全球稀土供應的主要來源之一。<br />\n<br />\n總理莫里森表示，要確保澳洲與世界各地的供應鏈緊密相連，這是澳洲的主權和戰略優先事項，必須是澳洲和合作夥伴可以依賴的供應鏈，因為稀土和關鍵礦物把未來會依賴的技術整合在一起。<br />\n<br />\n倡議措施包括協助企業利用國內豐富自然資源，在全球減碳的過程中開拓商機，鼓勵擴大電池和太陽能發電等高價值產品生產，以及令採礦更安全及高效的技術和設備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bannednews.org/2021/03/blog-post_38.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bannednews.org%2F2021%2F03%2Fblog-post_38.html&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWeddKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=e9ebc5b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bannednews.org/2021/03/blog-post_38.html</a>"},{"pid":"9438af1f16bdf5bed9dc529552decb0ffb5d3e1f","tid":2434737,"uid":171506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T17:14:22.000Z","msg":"希望民主國家爭氣，一齊合作"},{"pid":"f419b49a71b8b11a600e64370e62f2123babc14d","tid":2434737,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T17:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9d5d542150edd553ad6f0986cfcf49c8330438","tid":2434737,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T17:18:52.000Z","msg":"國際黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dccd21bf7c01f526125acde20d6cfdd36f3e2c13","tid":2434737,"uid":300877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T17:20:38.000Z","msg":"澳洲加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im